              'Our affinity skills are calibrated to reach 100% critical hit rate without tenderizing - particularly valuable against Alatreon where maintaining tenderized parts requires precise timing and positioning knowledge.',
              'The four-piece Fatalis armor grants both Transcendence for sharpness management and extended health/stamina caps, plus Inheritance to access skill secrets without restrictive armor combinations. This flexibility lets us incorporate both raw damage maximizers and comfort skills.',
              "AT Velkhana greaves round out the build with Peak Performance 3, adding substantial raw damage that's easily maintained through our health augment.",
            ],
            image: alatreonIce,
            imageAlt: 'Alatreon Ice Lance',
            stats: {
              raw: 804,
              sharpness: {
                hits: 60,
